{
  "texts": [
    "Furthermore, social and cultural factors may influence the way topics are perceived and the efficacy of countermeasures to limit the impact of misinformation [27, 28].",
    "While there exists a significant amount of literature addressing misinformation, only some studies examine its impact over time and across different countries [10, 29] or topics [30] [31] [32].",
    "However, to our knowledge, there has been no simultaneous investigation into all dimensions.",
    "Still, countries may exhibit different levels of sensibility and resilience to misinformation [33].",
    "This may depend on different factors, from intrinsic cultural variables to topic-dependent characteristics."
  ]
}